chan = Rails.configuration.slack_channels.horizons_sol

header "☀️ welcome to sol!"

section <<~TEXT, markdown: true
  You've just been added to <##{chan}>, the channel for Horizons Sol in South America! For more info, check out [horizons.hackclub.com/sol](https://horizons.hackclub.com/sol).

  Head over and introduce yourself!
TEXT
